precis:
Authorize the Secretary of State for External Affairs or Derek H. Burney
or L.H. Legault to sign an Agreement with the Government of the United
States in the form of an Exchange of Notes relating to the FM
Broadcasting Service in the 88-108 MHZ Frequency Band.
